--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project structure:

src/main/java:
	com.config:
		Config.properties
		
	com.pages:
		Login_Page.java
		Product_Page.java
		Cart_Page.java
		CheckOut_Page
			
	com.utility:
		Config.java
		ConfigReader.java
		ExcelReader.java
		ExtentReporterManager.java
		Utility.java
		
	testdata:
	     Expected_Result.xlsx	
		
src/test/java:
	apphooks:
		ApplicationHooks.java
	
	login_stepdefinitions:
		LoginPageSteps.java
		
	product_stepdefinitions:
	    Product_Step_Page.java
	    	
	cart_stepdefinitions:
	    Cart_Step_Page.java
	 
	outline_stepdefinitions:
	    Expected_Stepdefinitions.java
	    
	excel_stepdefinition:
	   Excel_StepDefinition.java       	
		
	testrunner:
		CartPage_TestRunner.java
	
	testrunner_excel:
	    Excel_TestRunner.java
	    
	testrunner_outline:
	    Outline_TestRunner.java    	
			
		
src/main/resources:
	ReadMe
						
src/test/resources:
	Features folder
		Cart1.feature
		CartOutline.feature
		Excel.feature
	testng.xml		

drivers folder:
	chromedriver.exe
	
extent_reports folder:

report:

	
	
screenshots folder:
	file.png	
	
pom.xml			
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project creation sequence:

Create maven project
Add the dependencies in pom.xml
Maven project will have 4 sections by default(if not then create them):
	src/main/java
	src/main/resources
	src/test/java
	src/test/resources

Create the required packages, classes, files in them as per below sequence:

Step 1 --> Create Feature file
Step 2 --> Create Config.java
Step 3 --> Create Config.properties
Step 4 --> Create ConfigReader.java
Step 5 --> Create Utility.java
Step 6 --> Create ExcelReader.java
Step 7 --> Create ExtentReportManager.java
Step 8 --> Create Login_Page.java
Step 9 --> Create Product_Page.java
Step 10 --> Create Cart_Page.java
Step 11 --> Create CheckOut_Page.java
Step 12 --> Create ApplicationHooks.java
Step 13 --> Create LoginPage_Step_Page.java
Step 14 --> Create ProductPage_Step_Page.java
Step 15 --> Create CartPage_Step_Page.java
Step 16 --> Create Excel_StepDefinitios.java
Step 17 --> Create expected_StepDefinitions.java
Step 16 --> Create Expected_Result.xlsx
Step 13 --> Create CartPage_TestRunner.java
Step 14 --> Create Excel_TestRunner.java
Step 15 --> Create Outline_TestRunner.java

Create the drivers folder and keep driver in it
Create the screenshots folder to keep screenshots in it
Run the tests by using Test class(individual test class) or pom.xml

See the reports in test-output folder(created by testng)
See the reports in target folder(created by maven)
